reviews.review_text: SMR is all over the place... stella sound and mix....
beyond description! great sound,killer friend of the devil wish i was there!FIVE STARS!

Decent Show- Great Sound Quality Very good Touch opener, rocky Stranger, rest of the 2nd set is solid. Set 2 is seemless, but the corrina starts off rocky, understandably since its a weird song and the first time they played it. The band just seems very confused, like they dont have a rally point. Good other one, and the rest of the 2nd set. Phil is really pulling the rest of the band for the show, he really shines in the 2nd set.
